<html>
    <body>
    <h1></h1>

    <p><%= @sender.fullname -%>, a member of the
    <%= link_to "NetLogo Modeling Commons", :controller => :account, :action => :mypage %>,
    thinks that the <%= @node.name %> model might be of interest to you.</p>

    <p>You can see this model for yourself by clicking
    <%= link_to "here", :controller => :browse, :action => :one_model, :id => @node.id %>.</p>

    <p><%= link_to "NetLogo", "http://ccl.northwestern.edu/netlogo" %>
    is a computer program that lets you create and view computerized
    models (i.e., simulations).  The
    <%= link_to "Modeling Commons", :controller => :account, :action => :mypage %>
    is a collaborative
    modeling Web site, allowing people with common interests to share
    models and modeling ideas with one another.</p>

    <p>Participation in the Modeling Commons is free of charge, and
    requires only that you register to participate.</p>

    </body>
